{{Infobox artefact
| name     = Statue of A'a from Rurutu
| image     = Handbook to the ethnographical collections (1910) (14596837587).jpg
| image_caption = The A'a Idol from Rurutu in the British Museum
| material   = Wood
| size     = 1.17 metres high
| created    = before 1821 (probably 1591–1647)
| location   = [[British Museum]], [[London]]
| registration = [https://www.britishmuseum.org/research/collection_online/collection_object_details.aspx?objectId=502783&partId=1 Oc,LMS.19]
